<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="275" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="275">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="275">
<taxonomicName authority="Walckenaer, 1805" authorityName="Framenau &amp; Baptista &amp; Oliveira &amp; Castanheira" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Framenau &amp; Baptista &amp; Oliveira &amp; Castanheira" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Arachnida" family="Araneidae" genus="Epeira" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Epeira flavicoma" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavicoma">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="275">Epeira flavicoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Simon, 1880 was described based on a female from New Caledonia. 
<bibRefCitation author="Simon, E" journalOrPublisher="Cladistics" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" refId="B42" refString="Simon, E, 1880. Materiaux pour servir a une faun arachnologique de la Nouvelle Caledonie. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 23 (C.R.): 164-175." title="Materiaux pour servir a une faun arachnologique de la Nouvelle Caledonie. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 23 (C. R.): 164 - 175." year="1880">Simon (1880)</bibRefCitation>
diagnosed the species at the time from 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Araneidae" genus="H." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="H. capitalis" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" rank="species" species="capitalis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="275">H. capitalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comb. nov. by colour differences. 
<bibRefCitation author="Berland, L" journalOrPublisher="Nova Caledonia, Zoologie" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" pagination="159 - 255" refId="B2" refString="Berland, L, 1924. Araigees de la Nouvelle-Caledonie et des Iles Loyalty. Nova Caledonia, Zoologie 3: 159 - 255" title="Araigees de la Nouvelle-Caledonie et des Iles Loyalty." volume="3" year="1924">Berland (1924)</bibRefCitation>
reported both species from New Caledonia, specifically the Loyalty Islands, and differentiated them both by colour and the length of the epigyne, being much longer in 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Araneidae" genus="H." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="H. flavicoma" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" rank="species" species="flavicoma">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="275">H. flavicoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comb. nov.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="275">
The detailed treatment of this species is not part of this project, but it is clear that 
<bibRefCitation author="Simon, E" journalOrPublisher="Cladistics" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" refId="B42" refString="Simon, E, 1880. Materiaux pour servir a une faun arachnologique de la Nouvelle Caledonie. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 23 (C.R.): 164-175." title="Materiaux pour servir a une faun arachnologique de la Nouvelle Caledonie. Annales de la Societe Entomologique de Belgique 23 (C. R.): 164 - 175." year="1880">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Simon’s">Simon's</normalizedToken>
(1880)
</bibRefCitation>
original description and 
<bibRefCitation author="Berland, L" journalOrPublisher="Nova Caledonia, Zoologie" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" pagination="159 - 255" refId="B2" refString="Berland, L, 1924. Araigees de la Nouvelle-Caledonie et des Iles Loyalty. Nova Caledonia, Zoologie 3: 159 - 255" title="Araigees de la Nouvelle-Caledonie et des Iles Loyalty." volume="3" year="1924">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Berland’s">Berland's</normalizedToken>
(1924)
</bibRefCitation>
depiction of the species conforms to the diagnosis of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Framenau &amp; Castanheira" authorityYear="2021" family="Araneidae" genus="Hortophora" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hortophora" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="275">Hortophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. nov., specifically with respect to the long epigyne scape. We therefore transfer the species to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Framenau &amp; Castanheira" authorityYear="2021" family="Araneidae" genus="Hortophora" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hortophora" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="275">Hortophora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. nov., 
<taxonomicName class="Arachnida" family="Araneidae" genus="H." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="H. flavicoma" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="275" rank="species" species="flavicoma">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="275">H. flavicoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
comb. nov., pending a revision of Pacific species of the genus.
</paragraph>
